{"tid":882235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"演唱被控　大媽：音樂唔係噪音","createTime":"2018-10-30T04:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T08:54:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dea368b0416a98caeb9af81f728da4501deed8e9","tid":882235,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181030/20533881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F20533881&d=VKt%2BBTUSQjqnA60UG1ack7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=bd16b5c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F20533881&h=117eacca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181030/20533881</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月30日 <br />\n<br />\n演唱被控　大媽：音樂唔係噪音<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181030/large/30la5p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181030%2Flarge%2F30la5p5.jpg&h=cd82cc5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾在旺角行人專用區唱歌的「新天地民族歌舞團」，團長兼主唱喻米英（圖）去年演唱期間，被票控擴音器造成的噪音煩擾罪。女團長批評警員因10多名途人展露厭惡表情而認為她的歌檔較討厭，因而票控她，她強調「音樂唔係噪音」，是令人心情舒暢的享受，如有人認為音樂聲屬煩擾，對所有表演者都不公平。案件下月5日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無透露用咪與觀眾互動<br />\n<br />\n案發於去年11月18日晚，被告喻米英在旺角西洋菜南街行人專用區，使用兩個各長1.5呎、闊1呎、高2呎的擴音器。警員接到投訴到場，當時有兩個歌唱攤檔，被告攤檔聲浪較大，她當時在唱「不知名的普通話歌」，警員觀察一會後票控被告，被告說：「我唔唱囉，畀次機會得唔得呀？」<br />\n<br />\n但是被告昨自辯時聲稱接下咪高峯後即遭票控，她承認有用咪問候歌迷，然後思考唱甚麼歌，但是一直沒有唱。<br />\n<br />\n喻在盤問下承認沒向法庭透露曾用咪與觀眾互動，但反駁指因裁判官只問她有否唱歌。被告陳詞時指當時附近有另外6個歌檔，質疑警員主觀地認為她的歌檔聲浪較大而票控她，沒先行勸喻，做法不講人情。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTS10224/18<br />\n■記者鄭語霆  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n與被告協議分賬　事主疑違律師守則<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n垃圾徵費測試　減廢僅10%　成效遜預期　四人家庭料月繳$66"},{"pid":"3af0c1bcdb0385bf6209bcb48ec6ba02d7208b4f","tid":882235,"uid":25148,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"噪音比較好聽"},{"pid":"0eb772a2b3707d8f936fcc2da31680b01e41213e","tid":882235,"uid":140309,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"音樂的確唔係噪音<br />\n<br />\n但你用乜撚野擴音器呀，屌你老母<br />\n你帶耳筒聽住唱唔撚得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175903a9643c5216dd4bf83bdd51542ba40205d5","tid":882235,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"947584143af8db55e972b1c14a27626461055603","tid":882235,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"老老實實，唔係燥音問題，係巿容問題"},{"pid":"423a0dcc1116c2225d39a9b44118e006ac10ec30","tid":882235,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"呢個媽好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f49592890fa98f792e4fea1e71b3c3706f4e0c","tid":882235,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"超時空要塞 大媽cross<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee1f1a91da8b61562f427bac31008a64bebc0de","tid":882235,"uid":4431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af0c1bcdb0385bf6209bcb48ec6ba02d7208b4f","tid":882235,"uid":25148,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"噪音比較好聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"控方律師，我贊成你嘅講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb69ca6c5f01a6d509c8b0222b274b9c96484e0","tid":882235,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"人哋揾十五萬一個月㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji